              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4644218075795783500">100% my recommendation for any high school that does an all-school read, especially any school that implements restorative justice. The whole book is about the fallacy of binaries - boy and girl, good and bad, guilt and innocence... none of these are polar opposites.</span>

          </span>
