              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6889743661518406503">This book surprised me more than I thought it would. A non fiction that reads like fiction (I had to remind myself a few times that this actually happened). You think it’s about a horrendous crime that occurs on a bus but you get a story of forgiveness and knowing who you are. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


